{"hash":"ffeaaa1294b3f47ae34ec59ddae2f11cbaec2faf","data":{"doc":{"title":"Installation","path":"/en/setup/installation/","date":"20. September 2022","content":"<p>This guide explains how to run Wakamiti quickly and verify that the installation works.</p>\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\"><a href=\"#prerequisites\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Prerequisites</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.docker.com/get-started/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Docker</a> installed and running.</li>\n<li>A project folder containing your <code class=\"language-text\">.feature</code> files and <code class=\"language-text\">wakamiti.yaml</code>.</li>\n<li>Internet access to download the Docker image and external dependencies.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"run-wakamiti-with-docker\"><a href=\"#run-wakamiti-with-docker\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Run Wakamiti with Docker</h2>\n<p>From your project folder, run:</p>\n<p>Windows:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><button onclick=\"copyToClipboard(this)\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-copy-icon\">\n    <path d=\"M0 6.75C0 5.784.784 5 1.75 5h1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-1.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.5 0v1.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 9.25 16h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 14.25Z\"></path><path d=\"M5 1.75C5 .784 5.784 0 6.75 0h7.5C15.216 0 16 .784 16 1.75v7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 14.25 11h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 5 9.25Zm1.75-.25a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-7.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25-.25Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n      <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-check-icon hidden\">\n    <path d=\"M13.78 4.22a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06l-7.25 7.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0L2.22 9.28a.751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018L6 10.94l6.72-6.72a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n                </button><pre class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> run <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--rm</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-v</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"%cd%:/wakamiti\"</span> wakamiti/wakamiti</pre><pre class=\"hidden\">docker run --rm -v &quot;%cd%:/wakamiti&quot; wakamiti/wakamiti</pre></div>\n<p>Linux:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><button onclick=\"copyToClipboard(this)\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-copy-icon\">\n    <path d=\"M0 6.75C0 5.784.784 5 1.75 5h1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-1.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.5 0v1.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 9.25 16h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 14.25Z\"></path><path d=\"M5 1.75C5 .784 5.784 0 6.75 0h7.5C15.216 0 16 .784 16 1.75v7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 14.25 11h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 5 9.25Zm1.75-.25a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-7.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25-.25Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n      <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-check-icon hidden\">\n    <path d=\"M13.78 4.22a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06l-7.25 7.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0L2.22 9.28a.751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018L6 10.94l6.72-6.72a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n                </button><pre class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> run <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--rm</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-v</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">pwd</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>:/wakamiti\"</span> --add-host<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>host.docker.internal:host-gateway wakamiti/wakamiti</pre><pre class=\"hidden\">docker run --rm -v &quot;$(pwd):/wakamiti&quot; --add-host=host.docker.internal:host-gateway wakamiti/wakamiti</pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"use-a-specific-wakamiti-version\"><a href=\"#use-a-specific-wakamiti-version\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Use a specific Wakamiti version</h2>\n<p>If you need a fixed version for reproducible runs:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><button onclick=\"copyToClipboard(this)\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-copy-icon\">\n    <path d=\"M0 6.75C0 5.784.784 5 1.75 5h1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-1.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.5 0v1.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 9.25 16h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 14.25Z\"></path><path d=\"M5 1.75C5 .784 5.784 0 6.75 0h7.5C15.216 0 16 .784 16 1.75v7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 14.25 11h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 5 9.25Zm1.75-.25a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-7.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25-.25Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n      <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-check-icon hidden\">\n    <path d=\"M13.78 4.22a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06l-7.25 7.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0L2.22 9.28a.751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018L6 10.94l6.72-6.72a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n                </button><pre class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> run <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--rm</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-v</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"%cd%:/wakamiti\"</span> wakamiti/wakamiti:<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>version<span class=\"token operator\">></span></pre><pre class=\"hidden\">docker run --rm -v &quot;%cd%:/wakamiti&quot; wakamiti/wakamiti:&lt;version&gt;</pre></div>\n<p>Available tags: <a href=\"https://hub.docker.com/r/wakamiti/wakamiti/tags\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Wakamiti Docker Hub</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"validate-the-installation\"><a href=\"#validate-the-installation\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Validate the installation</h2>\n<p>After execution, confirm:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The process ends with test results in the console.</li>\n<li>Output files are generated (for example, <code class=\"language-text\">wakamiti.json</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">wakamiti.html</code> if reporting is enabled).</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"next-steps\"><a href=\"#next-steps\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Next steps</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Learn the recommended configuration in <a href=\"/wakamiti//en/setup/configuration\">Configuration</a>.</li>\n<li>Follow the execution workflow in <a href=\"/wakamiti//en/setup/usage\">Usage</a>.</li>\n<li>Review full engine options in <a href=\"/wakamiti//en/wakamiti/architecture\">Architecture</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n"}},"context":{"id":"30c1d0277fecc21e5b49c188fe663f0e","path":"/en/setup/installation/","locale":"en"}}